## ğŸ’° Premium (Optional)

Want to accept crypto payments?

1. Get a wallet address from MetaMask: https://metamask.io/
2. Add to `.env`:
   ```env
   ENABLE_CRYPTO_PAYMENTS=true
   PAYMENT_WALLET_ADDRESS=0xyourwalletaddress
   ```
3. Restart bot
4. Users run `/premium subscribe` â†’ bot shows payment details
5. When they send USDC/USDT on Polygon â†’ auto-enabled!

See `SETUP_GUIDE.md` section "Step 4b: Setup Crypto Payments" for details.

## âš ï¸ Common First-Time Issues

### "Bot doesn't respond to /start"
- Wait 5 minutes (commands take time to register)
- Kick the bot and re-invite it
- Check bot has "Use Application Commands" permission

### "Cannot find module '@prisma/client'"
```powershell
npm run prisma:generate
```

### "Cannot login to Discord"
- Check your `DISCORD_TOKEN` in `.env` (no spaces/quotes)
- Verify token from Discord Developer Portal
- Make sure bot is enabled

### "Database errors"
```powershell
npm run prisma:push
```

**See SETUP_GUIDE.md "Common Issues" for more**

